summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the submission to the qualified electors (voters) of The City of Seattle at a special election requested to be held therein on November 5, 1974 of the initiative measure contemplated by voter's petition (C.F. 279658) relating to the former Sand Point Naval Air Station; providing for certification of such initiative measure to the Director of the Department of Records and Elections of King County and prescribing the ballot title therefor.
